instance.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="install-mcp-toolbox"&gt;Install MCP Toolbox&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download the latest version of Toolbox as a binary. Select the &lt;a href="https://github.com/googleapis/mcp-toolbox/releases"&gt;correct
binary&lt;/a&gt; corresponding
to your OS and CPU architecture. You are required to use Toolbox version
v0.15.0+:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle using MCP</title><link>https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/documentation/connect-to/ides/oracle_mcp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/documentation/connect-to/ides/oracle_mcp/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://modelcontextprotocol.io/introduction"&gt;Model Context Protocol (MCP)&lt;/a&gt; is
