&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/documentation/connect-to/ides/sqlite_mcp/#configure-your-mcp-client"&gt;Windsurf&lt;/a&gt; (Codium)&lt;/li&gt;
